Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越有夏天的感觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说日本的四季区分的很明显
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  夏天很热  冬天很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天和秋天气候舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国的天气倒是说变就变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常有一天就能体验四季的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里会突然下起雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然下起垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会下起可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国经常就会发生这样的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中暑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没那么热啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  夏天已经近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:01:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要珍惜这稍纵即逝的季节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九条可怜  夏日版本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜看起来好像刚修行结束的摇滚歌手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么物种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这套衣服的主题是狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你买来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我自己裁的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己裁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上还是有点冷的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那身无袖装是怎么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不好好穿制服小心又惹久世桥老师生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件衣服看起来超酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下估计连家长都要被叫来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎么这么老实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要叫家长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子  你的发型有点乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你拿包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当你的出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要硬撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心啦  我不会去打小报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的妈妈发起火来很恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实前些日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:36.71,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Karen! I've heard a rumor that you've been causing trouble for your homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:45.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,As a penalty, I will eat a piece of super yummy cake in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Please，have mercy on me！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}可怜  我听说你现在老给你们班主任添乱子啊  这很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}作为惩罚  我会在你面前吃一块超可口的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}您饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}没门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把你们俩拉下喽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久就是暑假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有将近2个月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈老是教导我要当个乖女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我吵吵闹闹的话  希望你们能提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么行  活泼才是可怜的亮点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜和爱丽丝都是我的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都像活在天堂里一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绫你也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  天使天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
