Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都穿上夏装了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很热嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你不穿一点凉快些的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这姑且也是夏装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道看上去让人感觉很热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我本来还以为你会换个形象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得夏天穿的可爱些比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩…玩偶装？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在橱柜里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说要穿凉快的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来试试看能不能在夏天穿着这件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  你为了我也太拼了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  今天我先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸给我买了我一直很想要的限定版项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说她爸给她买了条项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜和她爸爸关系真的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她很粘爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粘爸爸听起来不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快递？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  你不是先回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,OH there you are！I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I came all the way here as I am so shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,but dont worry, I already called mom.Please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,It's my dad. He was lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.89,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I really wanted to know the truth, even though he said it was for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,But he made me feel like an idiot for being pleased with his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I dislike  hate my bad! I'm not going to go home anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}各位  听我说  我超受打击的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}别急  我事先给妈妈打过电话了  总之听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}我爸他骗我  我只是想听他说实话可他居然说是为了我好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(960,1080)}但这样搞得我这么开心好像白痴一样  我讨厌  最讨厌爸爸了！我永远不回家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,900)}说的好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜她说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸大吵一架然后离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他说项链根本不可能买的到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说买回来也是骗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是不想看到我伤心的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善意的谎言时而越发伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这不能怪你爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是趁现在和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我今天就住在忍的家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  我已经和妈妈说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我没脸去见爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行啦  你突然来这么一出不是给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边倒是不能再欢迎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了  我不会给您添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个金发小女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊  随你住到什么时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连妈妈你也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  您今天拍完照想必也是很辛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来替你拿包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  怎么是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个角度不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是勇  怎么拍都是一张画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜居然离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老穿着制服可能会弄皱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就拿我的衣服给她穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是忍怎么穿都不合适的那件么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像是在做home stay一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很憧憬这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住在这里就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要住那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日式风味看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍的妈妈很擅长做和风菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈是英国人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以基本上做的菜都是西式的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿手菜是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉派
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道才是母亲的手艺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是做肉派的么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗茶淡饭不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦  坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我帮一帮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  别挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会让你一个人占尽风头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都从哪儿学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天感觉一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要是一个个洗肯定来不及所以大家一起洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜  洗发水挤太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般就这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我被排挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么小一个地方哪塞得进三个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍家里的浴室洗起来也很惬意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在这里倒是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你还是得和你爸爸好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我之后会打个电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜要是能和她爸爸和好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:45.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Dad? I'm sorry for getting angry, but I've calmed down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:51.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you so much! I love you,dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}爸爸  刚才对不起  我没在生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}真的  我最喜欢爸爸啦  爱死你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸用特权把那条项链给弄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸他果然好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我得和大家一起分享这份快乐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜？你怎么了？真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想送给小绫一份快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想送给阳子一份快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜你总是这么阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦  any day anytime anywhere 我都很阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜  你能和爸爸和好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都得感谢爱丽丝  果然爱丽丝是我的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  差不多该睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？好早  十点都不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜  想在我床上睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行  这是单人床  而且可怜的睡相很差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  让可怜靠墙睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就算我掉下去也一样身处天国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是地狱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天这次突然的留宿真让人开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你留我过夜  下次我请你来英国我家homestay吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍你应该也见过可怜的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大的哦  就像城堡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得应该是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都住过来也绰绰有余
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算住一百个人也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来感觉好像不是那么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该睡了  我关灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  爱丽丝  可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  忍  可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  可怜  把我的被子卷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快起床  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  再等十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我只等十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们有三个人呢  怎么都在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚我接到可怜的电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫你也接到了？我也接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也没什么特别重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  可怜  为什么你会和忍她们一起上学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家在反方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊  昨晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小开始  扮演英雄的就一直是爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？真是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  不是办家家酒吗  为什么玩怪兽游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是至今为止感觉都是可怜带着爱丽丝走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  现在她就像妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直都很尊敬爱丽丝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只认识homestay时的爱丽丝和现在的爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想听听爱丽丝小时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是小忍来英国homestay完回到日本以后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}来  爱丽丝  我们出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello alice.Let's go out and play
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝好像很忙的样子  在写五十音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是比较投入而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Alice. Are you studying japanese again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.71,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't have lesson with my dad today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}爱丽丝  你又在学日语了吗  今天爸爸不会教我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}回顾与练习是学习的要诀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Preparation and reviewing are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Ehhh. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}呃…看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}来吧  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}现在不行  我现在有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}真无聊  我好无聊  玩嘛  我没事做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}抱歉  回头再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}对了  爸爸拿到了一个有趣的日本游戏  我拿来给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,No now I'm always on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:37.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Ohhh. It's boring. I'm bored. Let's play. I have got nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:46.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Guess what! My dad has a fun japanese game. How we get it.
